raw_data.title: Partner/Director II
raw_data.description: Partner/Director II: Provides strong executive level management and direction. Possesses a broad understanding of the client’s industry. Has an extensive set of skills to solve the client’s problems. Knows the client’s industry, and helps the client visualize where they need to be in their particular industry. Serves in an advisory capacity, providing members of the project team and the client organization a level of quality review to help guide the project to remain on schedule and within budget.
